messages.speech:
If you are a student at Century College, you can view the availability of classes through your online registration account known as eServices.  To access your account, go to the eServices Login Page. https://eservices.minnstate.edu/eservices/login.html?campusid=304
In order to view and print the list of classes that you are registered for, you will also need to log into your eServices Account.
